name: full moon
description:
During the Full Moon meditation, I fly from the earth like a balloon full of gas in the sky and go into the ocean. I relax in the water like a fish and soar again in the sky and fly from the mountains, plains and galaxies And I go higher until I reach the realm of the Creator of the universe, and in all this way, the rays of the moonlight from the crown chakra are connected to me like a waterfall.
In this illustration, I tried to depict a corner of this meditation.
